cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.AI

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it focuses on language-brain encoding experiments and language models. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves evaluating the performance of language models. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as it involves analyzing fMRI datasets. It may also fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves analyzing brain responses, and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves evaluating the performance of AI models.
